{"tid":2222131,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Elon Musk：幾年後會將“Starlink”IPO","createTime":"2020-09-29T01:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T14:07:45.000Z","uid":295230,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"1298d9a4b2dabbf821d3119c997775ff1f14ed5a","tid":2222131,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:43:20.000Z","msg":"SpaceX公司稱，幾年後其「星鏈」（Starlink）衞星互聯網服務項目可能登陸美股市場。<br />\n<br />\n該公司CEO馬斯克（Elon Musk）週一在推特上重申：「我們可能會將&lsquo;星鏈項目&rsquo;IPO，不過只在未來幾年收入增長平穩可預測的情況下，因為公開市場不喜歡飄忽不定的現金流。」<br />\n馬斯克認為，「星鏈項目」是「SpaceX創造收入的關鍵途徑」。他去年曾估計，「星鏈」每年可以帶來300億美元的收入。早前他表示，「星鏈項目」潛在市場規模高達1萬億美元，預計可以從今年開始創收。<br />\n<br />\n在此之前，SpaceX領導層就一度討論過這一想法。今年2月SpaceX總裁Gwynne Shotwell曾表示，公司可能會將「星鏈項目」分拆上市。但馬斯克一個月後表示，公司並未將重心放在「星鏈項目」上市，而是致力於保住其「不破產」，並強調了2000年初衞星互聯網服務公司的稀缺性。這一表態淡化了市場預期。<br />\n<br />\n所謂「星鏈項目」指的是，SpaceX擬在2019年至2024年間在太空搭建由約1.2萬顆衞星組成的「星鏈」網絡，從太空向地球提供高速互聯網接入服務。<br />\n<br />\n按照SpaceX計劃，將發射12批火箭，把720顆「星鏈」衞星送入軌道。每一批發射任務都由60顆衞星組成，每顆衞星重約為260公斤。去年11月，首批衞星已經成功發射，迄今為止發射成功的衞星數量也已超過700顆。<br />\n<br />\nSpaceX今年7月向美國聯邦通信委員會(FCC)表示，目前正在建設一個地面站和用户終端系統，以將用户直接連接到其網絡，每月將有120顆衞星及數以千計的小型終端投入生產。<br />\n今年夏天，SpaceX對進行私下Beta測試。該公司最近表示，測試結果顯示，該網絡的網速足以支撐在線視頻、遊戲和流媒體電影。SpaceX表示，「星鏈」已經有了非常大的潛在需求，美國各地有「近70萬人」表示對該公司即將推出的服務感興趣。<br />\n<br />\n進一步公開測試之後，公司計劃今年年底前在美國北部和加拿大南部提供「星鏈條」作為商業服務，並計劃「2021年覆蓋全球」。"},{"pid":"f842de070dc59c794058ad22f35e371f7c9969ab","tid":2222131,"uid":14494,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:45:41.000Z","msg":"tesla+starlink+spacex=Ironman <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0c0990532ac58d4472dc6f76dfa1bcef9df110","tid":2222131,"uid":55533,"like":124,"dislike":5,"score":119,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:46:11.000Z","msg":"我們在美國的父，願人都尊你的名為鋼鐵俠，願你的space X降臨，願你的tesla，行在地上，如同starlink行在天上。我們晚晚炒的美股，今日分拆給我們；接上我們的大腦，如同我們接上電腦的接口。不要叫我們遇見熊市，救我們脫離貧窮；因為火星，地球，月球，全是你的，直到永遠。阿門。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5416d95145b886b82762596b3419ded58e869ca","tid":2222131,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天父<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e25352e4305a0d0e3397b61978e06e5984e8a27","tid":2222131,"uid":55533,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:48:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/09/28/elon-musk-spacex-will-probably-ipo-starlink-in-several-years.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2020%2F09%2F28%2Felon-musk-spacex-will-probably-ipo-starlink-in-several-years.html&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXNqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=edb342c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2020/09/28/elon-musk-spacex-will-probably-ipo-starlink-in-several-years.html</a><br />\n<br />\ntsla直上500usd<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f5086e745f28644e6fc3e1725e80508aecde54","tid":2222131,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f842de070dc59c794058ad22f35e371f7c9969ab","tid":2222131,"uid":14494,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:45:41.000Z","msg":"tesla+starlink+spacex=Ironman <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bo